thread.title: BRIEF-Santos Says Australia’s Offshore Petroleum Regulator Has Accepted Barossa-Caldita Offshore Project Proposal

title: BRIEF-Santos Says Australia’s Offshore Petroleum Regulator Has Accepted Barossa-Caldita Offshore Project Proposal

organizations.name: offshore petroleum regulator has accepted barossa-caldita offshore project proposal  45 am / updated

text: 45 AM / Updated 11 minutes ago BRIEF-Santos Says Australia’s Offshore Petroleum Regulator Has Accepted Barossa-Caldita Offshore Project Proposal Reuters Staff March 21 (Reuters) - Santos Ltd: * AUSTRALIA’S OFFSHORE PETROLEUM REGULATOR HAS ACCEPTED THE BAROSSA-CALDITA OFFSHORE PROJECT PROPOSAL * NATIONAL OFFSHORE PETROLEUM SAFETY AND ENVIRONMENTAL MANAGEMENT AUTHORITY HAS ACCEPTED THE JOINT VENTURE’S PROJECT PROPOSAL.
